        <a href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/what-is-crs-score" style="display:block;color:#9ca3af;font-size:13px;padding:3px 0;text-decoration:none" onmouseover="this.style.color='#f87171'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#9ca3af'">What is CRS Score?</a>
